      	    		What is ExchangeHunt?
      	    	</span>
      	    </div>
      	    <div class="row">
      	    	<blockquote>
      	    		Exchangehunt is a trusted community for student exchangers all around the world to connect with each other and build friendships. You can look up universities, countries and states to look for student exchange possibilities. Message anyone in the community to ask for travel buddies, party goers, basically anything!
      	    	</blockquote>
      	    </div>
      	    <div class="row">
      	    	<span class="avenir-85">
      	    		Who is it for?
      	    	</span>
      	    </div>
      	    <div class="row">
      	    	<blockquote>
      	    		Exchangehunt is for university students, whom are going on exchange or are currently in an exchange programme, who are looking for other fellow exchangers, regardless of nationality.
      	    	</blockquote>
      	    </div>
      	    <div class="row">
      	    	<span class="avenir-85">
      	    		I don’t have an exchange university yet! Can I still sign up for Exchangehunt?
      	    	</span>
      	    </div>
      	    <div class="row">
      	    	<blockquote>
      	    		Yes you can! Though this portal serves primarily students who are already going or on exchange, you may find some friendly people to ask about their exchange experience, etc.
      	    	</blockquote>
      	    </div>
      	    <div class="row">
      	    	<span class="avenir-85">
      	    		Why exchangehunt instead of traditional Facebook group?
      	    	</span>
      	    </div>
      	    <div class="row">
      	    	<blockquote>
      	    		We recognise that typical Facebook group is only limited within each tertiary institution and there’s no channel for people to reach out to other exchangers of other universities in the same region. So Exchangehunt allows people from different universities to connect with one another while on exchange.
      	    	</blockquote>
      	    </div>
      	    <div class="row">
      	    	<span class="avenir-85">
      	    		What are shoutouts?
      	    	</span>
      	    </div>
      	    <div class="row">
      	    	<blockquote>
      	    		Shoutouts are basically an announcement function where you can post anything to the entire community. 
      	    	</blockquote>
      	    </div>
      	    <div class="row">
